                                <p class="text-muted">Find out what people see and say about this event, and join the conversation.</p>
                                <p>Use this hashtag: <a t-att-href="'http://twitter.com/search?q=%23'+event.twitter_hashtag" target="_blank">#<span t-field="event.twitter_hashtag"/></a></p>
                            </div> -->
